snippet.title: HELLRIDER - Official Gameplay Trailer 2 (VER 0.9)
snippet.description:
A small video showcasing the overall gameplay pace and upcoming changes for the new version of HELLRIDER, a work in progress Doom mod that puts you in the shoes of Rachel "Hellrider" Williams, an angry lady with a certain affinity with guns.

Grab it here!: https://forum.zdoom.org/viewtopic.php?f=43&t=68575

Music: Carpenter Brut - Turbo Killer

Map Packs used in this video:
Back to Saturn X: https://www.moddb.com/mods/back-to-saturn-x
Brutal Doom 64: https://www.moddb.com/mods/brutal-doom-64/downloads/brutal-doom-64-version-10
Epic 2: https://www.moddb.com/games/doom-ii/addons/epic-2
